    <element name="Toll Sentinel" type="Archetype" source="The Wyrmslayer" id="ID_PW_WS_ARCHETYPE_WYRMSLAYER_TOLLSENTINEL">
        <supports>wyrmslayer-pledge</supports>
        <description>
            <p>Earning their name from the toll taken when attempting to pass them in combat, Toll Sentinels are bulwarks dedicated to protecting their allies and staying alive. Being the only pledge trained in heavy armour and the usage of shields, Toll sentinels have adapted their leap to be a defensive tool, controlling the battlefield through sheer force of will to hold position. A Toll Sentinel will always stay alive. After all, if you aren’t dead, your enemy hasn’t won yet.</p>
            <p class="indent"></p>
            <div element="ID_PW_WS_ARCHETYPE_FEATURE_WYRMSLAYER_TOLLSENTINEL_DEFENDERS_ARSENAL" />
            <div element="ID_PW_WS_ARCHETYPE_FEATURE_WYRMSLAYER_TOLLSENTINEL_IRON_WILL" />
            <div element="ID_PW_WS_ARCHETYPE_FEATURE_WYRMSLAYER_TOLLSENTINEL_DEFENSIVE_STANCE" />
            <div element="ID_PW_WS_ARCHETYPE_FEATURE_WYRMSLAYER_TOLLSENTINEL_HEROIC_LEAP" />
            <div element="ID_PW_WS_ARCHETYPE_FEATURE_WYRMSLAYER_TOLLSENTINEL_PROTECTORS_PRESENCE" />
            <div element="ID_PW_WS_ARCHETYPE_FEATURE_WYRMSLAYER_TOLLSENTINEL_CROWD_CONTROL" />
            <div element="ID_PW_WS_ARCHETYPE_FEATURE_WYRMSLAYER_TOLLSENTINEL_DRAGONS_TERROR" />
            <div element="ID_PW_WS_ARCHETYPE_FEATURE_WYRMSLAYER_TOLLSENTINEL_PROTECT_THE_WEAK" />
        </description>
        <sheet display="false">
            <description></description>
        </sheet>
        <rules>
            <grant type="Archetype Feature" id="ID_PW_WS_ARCHETYPE_FEATURE_WYRMSLAYER_TOLLSENTINEL_DEFENDERS_ARSENAL" level="3" />
            <grant type="Archetype Feature" id="ID_PW_WS_ARCHETYPE_FEATURE_WYRMSLAYER_TOLLSENTINEL_IRON_WILL" level="3" />
