        <supports>Weapon, Melee, ID_INTERNAL_DAMAGE_TYPE_PIERCING, ID_INTERNAL_WEAPON_PROPERTY_REACH, ID_INTERNAL_WEAPON_PROPERTY_FINESSE, defenders-arsenal</supports>
    </element>
    
    <element name="Greatshield" type="Weapon" source="The Wyrmslayer" id="ID_PW_WS_WEAPON_GREATSHIELD">
        <supports>ID_INTERNAL_DAMAGE_TYPE_PIERCING,  ID_INTERNAL_WEAPON_PROPERTY_REACH, ID_INTERNAL_WEAPON_PROPERTY_FINESSE, ID_INTERNAL_WEAPON_GROUP_DEFENDERS_ARSENAL</supports>
        <description>
            <p>A chain grappling hook with a dagger style blade on the end. Expands when latching into a target. Effective for clinging to moving enemies. When you hit a creature with an attack, you can choose latch on to them. The creature can use its action to remove the latch. When the creature moves when latched this way, you can move with them at their speed without provoking opportunity attacks.</p>
        </description>
        <setters>
            <set name="category">Weapons</set>
            <set name="slot">onehand</set>
            <set name="damage" type="piercing">1d10</set>
            <set name="proficiency">ID_PROFICIENCY_WEAPON_PROFICIENCY_GREATSHIELD</set>
        </setters>
    </element>
